(724, 1, '2016-02-13 12:24:34', '2016-02-13 12:24:34', '[vc_row full_height="yes" parallax="1" fullwidth="1" css=".vc_custom_1457012831431{background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/workwithme.jpg?id=1013) !important;}" el_class="custom-parallax"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-content"][vc_column_text]“CHANGE YOUR LIFE TODAY.\r\nDON’T GAMBLE ON THE FUTURE,\r\nACT NOW, WITHOUT DELAY.”\r\n<span class="custom-author">-SIMONE DE BEAUVOIR</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]I help my clients connect with the greatest version of themselves. To create impact in their life’s work. To be more present and in love with the life that they are choosing for themselves. Whatever their walk of life, current occupation or aspirations.\r\n\r\nI trained as a coach with the prestigious <a href="http://www.thecoaches.com/" target="_blank">Coaches Training Institute</a> (CTI) and am currently undergoing its rigorous certification programme to become certified by the <a href="http://www.coachfederation.org/" target="_blank">International Coach Federation</a>.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Clarity Session"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]A 2-hour session to get crystal clear on what’s important to you and the choices you need to make to move into action and get what you want.\r\n\r\nThis is a structured session using tried and tested CTI tools to help you get unstuck and choose from the powerful perspective of who you truly are and what you value the most. Our values are what we draw power from to guide us through the decisions we have to make in life, whether it’s work- or life-related, big or small. Together, we will identify your values and get really clear on what it is you really want.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column el_class="custom-workme-btn"][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Clarity Session: £300[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]If you want deeper, more sustainable change and want to carry on working together after your Clarity Session, the value of your Session will be offset against the value of the coaching package you buy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Ongoing coaching"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]Change takes time. It can be daunting. And it’s more likely to actually happen with the right support. I work on an ongoing basis with clients who want big or deep change to live a juicy, meaningful and purposeful life. I help them to clarify what that means for them and connect to their inner strength and clarity to create the impact that they want to see in the world.\r\n\r\nI typically work with clients twice a month for a minimum period of 3 months, or longer.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Sign up for 8 sessions: £1,125[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Sign up for 14 sessions: £1,560[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact%2F||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][vc_column_text](A 15% discount is offered to advance payments in full.)[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Work with me', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'work-with-me', '', '', '2016-03-03 14:33:49', '2016-03-03 14:33:49', '', 0, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/?page_id=724', 0, 'page', '', 0),
