(862, 1, '2016-02-27 06:46:23', '2016-02-27 06:46:23', '[vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="What is coaching?"][vc_column_text]Imagine you wanted to learn to ride a bike and you had the choice between a therapist, a consultant and a coach. How do you decide which one is best for you?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The therapist will approach the bike with you and ask you how it makes you feel and what associations you have with bikes from childhood.</li>\r\n	<li>The consultant will get on the bike for you, ride it and then write a report setting out how best to ride it.</li>\r\n	<li>The coach will tell you to get on the bike and will stay right by your side until you can ride it on your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'What is coaching', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-27 06:46:23', '2016-02-27 06:46:23', '', 17, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
