(874, 1, '2016-02-29 06:51:05', '2016-02-29 06:51:05', '[vc_row full_height="yes" fullwidth="1" nospacing="1" el_class="custom-slider-home1" css=".vc_custom_1455689540254{padding-left: 0px !important;}"][vc_column width="3/4"][rev_slider_vc alias="home-page"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4" el_class="custom-slider-aboutme"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>About Me</h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="700" img_size="190 x 190" style="vc_box_circle_2" css=".vc_custom_1456138289119{border-radius: 1px !important;}" el_class="custom-about-circle"][vc_column_text]I wanted to be an actress when i was younger. My parents thought that wasn''t very sensible, so I ended up studying law instead.\n\nI wanted to be an actress when i was younger.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="CONTINUE READING" style="flat" shape="square" color="inverse" size="xs" align="center" link="url:http%3A%2F%2F192.168.0.130%2Fswitchedoncoaching.com%2Fabout-me%2F|title:About%20me|target:%20_blank"][vc_raw_html]JTNDaHIlMjAlMkYlM0U=[/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="custom-block-1"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="20px"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="custom-subblock"][vc_single_image image="703" alignment="center" el_class="custom-block-img"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>WORK WITH ME</h2>\nA 2-hour session, face-to-face in London or on the phone/Skype, to get crystal clear on what’s important to you and the choices you need to make to move into action and get what you want.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="READ MORE" style="flat" shape="square" color="purple" size="xs" align="center" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fwork-with-me|title:Work%20with%20me|target:%20_blank"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="custom-subblock"][vc_single_image image="703" alignment="center" el_class="custom-block-img"][vc_column_text]\n<h2>BELIEFS</h2>\nMaking shit happen, Laughter until mascara runs down my cheeks, The incredibleness of the universe, Bright colours and sparkl