(877, 1, '2016-02-27 09:36:58', '2016-02-27 09:36:58', '[vc_row full_height="yes" parallax="1" fullwidth="1" css=".vc_custom_1456319159426{background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Clouds.jpg?id=752) !important;}" el_class="custom-parallax"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-right"][vc_column_text css_animation="right-to-left"]We create our reality by choosing what we focus our attention on.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Clarity Session"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]A 2-hour session, face-to-face in London or on the phone/Skype, to get crystal clear on what’s important to you and the choices you need to make to move into action and get what you want.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="workme-right-content"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]Face-to-face – value: £350\r\n\r\nPhone/Skype – value: £300[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]If you want deeper, more sustainable change and want to carry on working together after your Clarity Session, the value of the Session will be offset against the value of any package you buy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Ongoing coaching"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]The work I do is different with every client I work with because everyone is different. But whatever their walk of life, current occupation or aspirations, I help all of them to connect to the greatest version of themselves. To be more present and in love with the life that they are choosing for themselves.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="workme-right-content"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]Buy a package of 6 sessions – value: £150/hour\r\n\r\nBuy a package of 12 sessions – value: £130/hour[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Work with me', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '724-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-27 09:36:58', '2016-02-27 09:36:58', '', 724, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(878, 1, '2016-02-27 09:53:10', '2016-02-27 09:53:10', '[vc_row full_height="yes" parallax="1" fullwidth="1" el_class="custom-parallax" css=".vc_custom_1456557675337{background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Clouds.jpg?id=752) !important;}"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-right"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]Comfort zones are like cats: they like to stretch.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="custom-coaching"][vc_column][ewf-headline title="What is coaching?"][vc_column_text]Imagine you wanted to learn to ride a bike and you had the choice between a therapist, a consultant and a coach. How do you decide which one is best for you?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The therapist will approach the bike with you and ask you how it makes you feel and what associations you have with bikes from childhood.</li>\r\n	<li>The consultant will get on the bike for you, ride it and then write a report setting out how best to ride it.</li>\r\n	<li>The coach will tell you to get on the bike and will stay right by your side until you can ride it on your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'What is coaching', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-27 09:53:10', '2016-02-27 09:53:10', '', 17, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
