(939, 1, '2016-03-02 10:57:28', '2016-03-02 10:57:28', 'My coaching sessions with Valerie have been an illuminating journey which I am very grateful to have taken. I decided to try coaching because I wanted to make some changes in my life and career, but felt unsure about how to proceed. Right from the start, I found Valerie to be intuitive, easy to talk to and focused. Her open mindedness meant that our conversations felt natural and creative and the ideas that flowed from them spurred me to take actions which have had a very positive impact on my life and outlook. Highly recommended!', 'My coaching sessions', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '939', '', '', '2016-03-03 11:10:46', '2016-03-03 11:10:46', '', 0, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/?post_type=testimonials-widget&#038;p=939', 0, 'testimonials-widget', '', 0),
(940, 1, '2016-03-02 11:04:00', '2016-03-02 11:04:00', 'Having Valerie as a coach was so valuable to me, and completely surpassed my expectations. In less than 6 months, I had not only gained clarity about the direction I wanted to move in with my career, but I ended up being offered a job in exactly the area I had identified (and Valerie was one of the first people I told when I heard the news, after my husband and my mother!). That was an incredible, tangible outcome for me and the coaching was exactly what I needed to help me get there. But coaching also gave me lots of other intangible things like the confidence to trust my instincts, the ability to take a step back from my situation and assess it from a more objective position, and mechanisms to trust in my abilities and strengths even when I’m feeling wobbly.\r\n\r\nI would wholeheartedly recommend coaching with Valerie – she is very skilled at supporting people to become the best version of themselves and I will always be grateful for her support at a pivotal time in my career and life.', 'Recommend coaching', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '940', '', '', '2016-03-08 05:32:03', '2016-03-08 05:32:03', '', 0, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/?post_type=testimonials-widget&#038;p=940', 0, 'testimonials-widget', '', 0),
(941, 1, '2016-03-02 11:06:53', '2016-03-02 11:06:53', 'Initially my work with Valerie was targeted at getting over a rut I had gotten into launching my own Social Enterprise. What was incredible about the work that we did together, was in that Valerie supported me to take control of the situation. Once I realized through our sessions that I had made the personal choice to spread myself thin, and only through prioritizing and choosing where to spend my energy would I be able to achieve what I wanted, it all became easier. Valerie’s personable but direct style meant that I was able to be more honest with myself, and gave me someone objective to process with.\r\n\r\nIt felt like the clear goal setting and accountability made me consciously take responsibility for doing what needed to be done in my life. I’ve grown so much and learnt so much whilst she was working with me, and I really do believe that she has a unique insight that many other coaches would only dream of acquiring.', 'Initially my work with Valerie', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '941', '', '', '2016-03-03 11:13:16', '2016-03-03 11:13:16', '', 0, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/?post_type=testimonials-widget&#038;p=941', 0, 'testimonials-widget', '', 0),
