(962, 1, '2016-03-03 07:20:21', '2016-03-03 07:20:21', '[vc_row full_height="yes" parallax="1" fullwidth="1" css=".vc_custom_1456752224410{background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/work_with_me_banner.jpg?id=913) !important;}" el_class="custom-parallax"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-content"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">"Change your life today. Don’t gamble on the future, act now, without delay.”</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">- Simone de Beauvoir</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]I help my clients connect with the greatest version of themselves. To create impact in their life’s work. To be more present and in love with the life that they are choosing for themselves. Whatever their walk of life, current occupation or aspirations.\r\n\r\nI trained as a coach with the prestigious <a href="http://www.thecoaches.com/" target="_blank">Coaches Training Institute</a> (CTI) and am currently undergoing its rigorous certification programme to become certified by the <a href="http://www.coachfederation.org/" target="_blank">International Coach Federation</a>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Clarity Session"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]A 2-hour session, face-to-face in London or on the phone/Skype, to get crystal clear on what’s important to you and the choices you need to make to move into action and get what you want.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="workme-right-content"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]Face-to-face – value: £350\r\n\r\nPhone/Skype – value: £300[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]If you want deeper, more sustainable change and want to carry on working together after your Clarity Session, the value of the Session will be offset against the value of any package you buy.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Find out More" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact%2F||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Ongoing coaching"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text]The work I do is different with every client I work with because everyone is different. But whatever their walk of life, current occupation or aspirations, I help all of them to connect to the greatest version of themselves. To be more present and in love with the life that they are choosing for themselves.[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Find out More" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact%2F||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="workme-right-content"][vc_column_text css_animation="left-to-right"]Buy a package of 6 sessions – value: £150/hour\r\n\r\nBuy a package of 12 sessions – value: £130/hour[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Work with me', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '724-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-03 07:20:21', '2016-03-03 07:20:21', '', 724, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
