_class="custom-workme-btn"][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Clarity Session: £300[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]If you want deeper, more sustainable change and want to carry on working together after your Clarity Session, the value of your Session will be offset against the value of the coaching package you buy.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="Ongoing coaching"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text]Change takes time. It can be daunting. And it’s more likely to actually happen with the right support. I work on an ongoing basis with clients who want big or deep change to live a juicy, meaningful and purposeful life. I help them to clarify what that means for them and connect to their inner strength and clarity to create the impact that they want to see in the world.\r\n\r\nI typically work with clients twice a month for a minimum period of 3 months, or longer.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Sign up for 8 sessions: £1,125[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="workme-content"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="custom-Session"]Sign up for 14 sessions: £1,560[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Book Now" style="flat" shape="square" color="violet" size="xs" link="url:http%3A%2F%2Fswitchedon.addwebprojects.com%2Fcontact%2F||target:%20_blank" el_class="custom-btn-work"][vc_column_text](A 15% discount is offered to advance payments in full.)[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Work with me', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '724-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-03 14:33:49', '2016-03-03 14:33:49', '', 724, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/724-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
