(1045, 1, '2016-03-08 05:29:48', '2016-03-08 05:29:48', 'Having Valerie as a coach was so valuable to me, and completely surpassed my expectations. In less than 6 months, I had not only gained clarity about the direction I wanted to move in with my career, but I ended up being offered a job in exactly the area I had identified (and Valerie was one of the first people I told when I heard the news, after my husband and my mother!). That was an incredible, tangible outcome for me and the coaching was exactly what I needed to help me get there. But coaching also gave me lots of other intangible things like the confidence to trust my instincts, the ability to take a step back from my situation and assess it from a more objective position, and mechanisms to trust in my abilities and strengths even when I’m feeling wobbly.\n\nI would wholeheartedly recommend coaching with Valerie – she is very skilled at supporting people to become the best version of themselves and I will always be grateful for her support at a pivotal time in my career and life.', 'Recommend coaching', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '940-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-03-08 05:29:48', '2016-03-08 05:29:48', '', 940, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/940-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
