(1052, 1, '2016-03-08 08:02:11', '2016-03-08 08:02:11', '[vc_row parallax="1" fullwidth="1" el_class="custom-parallax" css=".vc_custom_1457012392122{margin-left: 0px !important;border-left-width: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/beliefs.jpg?id=1006) !important;}"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-content beliefs"][vc_column_text]“WE CREATE OUR REALITY BY CHOOSING\r\nWHAT WE FOCUS OUR ATTENTION ON.”[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ewf-headline title="I believe in"][vc_column_text el_class="custom-belief-content"]Making shit happen\r\n\r\nLaughter until mascara runs down my cheeks\r\n\r\nThe incredibleness of the universe\r\n\r\nBright colours and sparkly things\r\n\r\nStretching my comfort zone[/vc_column_text][ewf-headline title="For you, I believe in"][vc_column_text el_class="custom-belief-content"]The most magnificent version of you\r\n\r\nYour power to create your own reality\r\n\r\nYour ability to take care of yourself\r\n\r\nYour right to ask for what you want\r\n\r\nYour longing to act from the heart[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Beliefs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '775-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-08 08:02:11', '2016-03-08 08:02:11', '', 775, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/775-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1054, 1, '2016-03-08 08:10:27', '2016-03-08 08:10:27', '[vc_row full_height="yes" parallax="1" fullwidth="1" el_class="custom-parallax" css=".vc_custom_1457424555572{background-image: url(http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/whatiscoaching-1.jpg?id=1053) !important;}"][vc_column el_class="custom-parallax-content coaching"][vc_column_text]“TO LIVE IS TO CHOOSE. BUT TO CHOOSE WELL,\r\nYOU MUST KNOW WHO YOU ARE\r\nAND WHAT YOU STAND FOR.”\r\n<span class="custom-author">-KOFI ANNAN</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="custom-coaching"][vc_column][ewf-headline title="What is coaching?"][vc_column_text]Imagine you wanted to learn to ride a bike and you had the choice between a therapist, a consultant and a coach. How do you decide which one is best for you?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The therapist will approach the bike with you and ask you how it makes you feel and what associations you have with bikes from childhood.</li>\r\n	<li>The consultant will get on the bike for you, ride it and then write a report setting out how best to ride it.</li>\r\n	<li>The coach will tell you to get on the bike and will stay right by your side until you can ride it on your own.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'What is coaching', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-08 08:10:27', '2016-03-08 08:10:27', '', 17, 'http://switchedon.addwebprojects.com/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
